%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gold%20prices%20hit%20record%20high%20as%20expectations%20rise%20for%20the%20to%20Fed%20cut%20interest%20rates%20in%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225786%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20display%20at%20Agosi%20AG%20in%20Pforzheim%20is%20a%20gold%20bar%20that%20weighs%2012.5%20kilograms%20(400%20ounces)%2C%20has%20a%20fine%20gold%20content%20of%2099.99%20percent%20and%20lies%20on%20gold%20granules.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656dd3db58e7c0c29a291ca3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222893%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Egold%20bar%3Cp%3EUli%20Deck%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGold%20prices%20hit%20a%20record%20high%20of%20%242%2C152.30%20per%20ounce%20on%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20NYMEX%20continuous%20gold%20contract.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20price%20of%20gold%20has%20been%20steadily%20rising%20in%202023%2C%20with%20the%20commodity%20up%2014%25%20year%20to%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rally%20comes%20as%20investors%20price%20in%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20prices%20hit%20a%20record%20high%20on%20Monday%20as%20investors%20prepare%20for%20potential%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NYMEX%20Gold%20Continuous%20Contract%20peaked%20at%20%242%2C152.30%20per%20ounce%20on%20Monday%2C%20before%20paring%20gains%20to%20around%20%242%2C087.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prior%20intraday%20record%20high%20was%20different%20across%20different%20datasets%2C%20but%20they%20all%20went%20back%20to%202020.%20According%20to%20Dow%20Jones%20Market%20Data%2C%20it%20was%20%242%2C089.20.%20For%20Refinitiv%2C%20it%20was%20%242%2C072.50%2C%20while%20Bloomberg%20put%20it%20at%20%242%2C075.47.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20prices%20are%20up%2014%25%20year%20to%20date.%20But%20most%20of%20those%20gains%20have%20occurred%20since%20early%20October%20as%20the%20metal%20was%20trading%20sideways%20throughout%20most%20of%202023%20until%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20surge%20has%20been%20supercharged%20by%20increasing%20expectations%20among%20investors%20that%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20is%20not%20only%20done%20with%20its%20interest%20rate%20hiking%20regime%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-slowdown-interest-rates-outlook-federal-reserve-cuts-next-year-2023-11%5C%22%3Ethat%20it%20could%20cut%20interest%20rates%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CME%20Fed%20Watch%20Tool%20currently%20projects%20that%20the%20Fed%20will%20institute%20its%20first%20rate%20cut%20at%20its%20FOMC%20meeting%20in%20March%20with%20next%20year's%20cuts%20totaling%20125%20basis%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20economists%20expect%20even%20more%20cuts.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-slowdown-interest-rates-outlook-federal-reserve-cuts-next-year-2023-11%5C%22%3EING%20forecasts%20150%20basis%20points%20in%202024%20and%20a%20further%20100%20basis%20points%20of%20rate%20cuts%20in%202025.%3C%2Fa%3E%20If%20those%20predictions%20prove%20correct%2C%20gold%20prices%20might%20not%20be%20done%20rising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20alternative%20like%20cash%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20less%20appealing%20to%20investors%20as%20interest%20rates%20start%20to%20fall.%20Gold%20prices%20also%20tend%20to%20rise%20when%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20is%20in%20easing%20mode%2C%20whether%20it's%20cutting%20interest%20rates%20or%20increasing%20its%20balance%20sheet%2C%20on%20fears%20of%20potential%20inflation%20as%20well%20as%20the%20long-term%20effects%20that%20easing%20could%20have%20on%20the%20stability%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%20and%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20%3Ca%20h