ns%20of%20views.%20But%20internet%20sleuths%20have%20also%20played%20an%20increasing%20role%20in%20mysteries%20that%20unfold%20in%20real-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvan-life-mental-health-girl-isolation-challenges-gabby-petito-missing-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evan%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20influencer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fgabby-petito-brian-laundrie-missing-found-true-crime-tiktok-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGabby%20Petito%20went%20missing%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August%202021%2C%20social%20media%20was%20flooded%20with%20information%20about%20her%20disappearance%2C%20and%20theories%20about%20what%20may%20have%20happened%20to%20her.%20Some%20content%20played%20a%20part%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fgabby-petito-tiktok-viral-posts-brian-laundrie-disappearance-criticism-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20her%20case%20solved%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKendal%20Stoneystreet%2C%20an%20associate%20lecturer%20in%20criminology%20and%20sociology%20at%20Sheffield%20Hallam%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20this%20fascination%20with%20unfolding%20events%20is%20unsurprising%20because%20humans%20are%20particularly%20interested%20in%20%26quot%3Banything%20psychologically%20morbid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20watch%20these%20frightening%20experiences%20from%20the%20safety%20of%20our%20homes%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20vicariously%20experience%20through%20TV%20or%20films%2C%20and%20now%20TikToks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20that%20people%20can%20consume%20detailed%20overviews%20in%20bitesize%20chunks%20on%20apps%20like%20TikTok%2C%20Stoneystreet%20added%2C%20which%20she%20has%20observed%20many%20of%20her%20students%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoi's%20videos%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20are%20informative%20and%20packed%20full%20of%20sources%20and%20references%2C%20and%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes%20long%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStoneystreet%20told%20BI%20the%20problem-solving%20element%20is%20something%20that%20attracts%20people%20to%20true%20crime%2C%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20the%20disappearance%20of%20Madeline%20McCann%2C%20or%20even%20Jack%20the%20Ripper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20desensitization%20to%20true%20crime%2C%20due%20to%20our%20constant%20consumption%20of%20media%2C%20means%20it's%20almost%20a%20challenge%20or%20a%20game%20to%20solve%20these%20puzzles%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20satisfying%20when%20our%20predictions%20or%20suspicions%20are%20confirmed%20as%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20phenomenon%20has%20been%20coined%20%26quot%3Bthe%20curious%20case%20of%20the%20armchair%20detective%26quot%3B%20by%20criminologist%20Professor%20David%20Wilson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22tiktok%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20cite%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40crimewithkourt%2Fvideo%2F7303704370196008234%5C%22%20data-video-id%3D%5C%227303704370196008234%5C%22%20data-embed-from%3D%5C%22oembed%5C%22%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40crimewithkourt%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%40crimewithkourt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40crimewithkourt%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cp%3E%F0%9F%9A%A8Nancy%20Ng%20is%20STILL%20missing.%20These%20are%20the%20newest%20updates%20as%20of%2011%2F20..%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftruecrime%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22truecrime%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23truecrime%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftruecrimecommunity%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22truecrimecommunity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23truecrimecommunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%