0or%20exaggerated.%20Some%20spread%20outright%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-people-believe-conspiracy-theory-overconfidence-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econspiracy%20theories%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20add%20no%20aid%20to%20active%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20TikTok%20coverage%20on%20Nancy%20Ng%2C%20the%20ones%20with%20the%20most%20likes%20include%20those%20covering%20conspiracies%20like%20her%20death%20being%20a%20cult-based%20sacrifice%20or%20an%20elaborately%20coordinated%20hate%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20Stoneystreet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20is%20often%20forgotten%20that%20there%20are%20real%20people%20and%20families%20behind%20the%20stories%2C%20who%20may%20not%20be%20happy%20about%20strangers%20profiting%20off%20their%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20October%2C%20a%20man%20named%20Lawrence%20Crook%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fman-begs-tiktokers-stop-making-true-crime-about-mom-murder-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebegged%20TikTokers%20to%20stop%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20true%20crime%20content%20about%20his%20mom's%20murder.%20Odessa%20Carey%2C%2073%2C%20was%20murdered%20by%20her%20mentally%20ill%20daughter%2C%20Crook's%20sister%2C%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20later%2C%20people%20on%20TikTok%20are%20still%20making%20videos%20about%20the%20case%2C%20so%20Crook%20spoke%20to%20Chronicle%20Live%20about%20what%20that%20was%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20see%20it%20as%20entertainment%2C%20to%20see%20how%20many%20likes%20they%20can%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20Crook%20told%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20need%20to%20stop%20and%20think%20about%20the%20real%20families%20behind%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStoneystreet%20said%20cases%20that%20go%20viral%20tend%20to%20feature%20a%20particular%20type%20of%20victim%3A%20a%20young%2C%20attractive%20white%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20interesting%20about%20the%20case%20of%20Nancy%20Ng%20is%20that%20this%20is%20a%20woman%20of%20Asian%20descent%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20much%20of%20the%20rhetoric%20surrounding%20the%20case%20from%20Asian%20creators%20and%20other%20creators%20of%20color%20is%20how%20Nancy%20Ng's%20story%20should%20receive%20similar%20visibility%20to%20that%20of%20Gabby%20Petito's.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%20has%20occurred%20before.%20In%20January%202022%2C%20TikTokers%20criticized%20the%20media%20and%20the%20public%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftiktokers-criticize-lack-of-media-coverage-lauren-smith-fields-death-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lack%20of%20attention%20on%20Lauren%20Smith-Fields%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Black%20woman%20who%20was%20found%20dead%20after%20a%20Bumble%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20many%20referenced%20a%20phenomenon%20sociologists%20call%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fexperts-missing-women-of-color-are-not-centered-news-coverage-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emissing%20white%20woman%20syndrome%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20cases%20of%20missing%20white%20women%20and%20girls%20are%20far%20more%20likely%20to%20make%20the%20news%20than%20women%20of%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20creators%20including%20Choi%2C%20and%20true%20crime%20podcaster%20Kourtney%20Nichole%20who%20has%201.2%20million%20followers%2C%20have%20managed%20to%20increase%20awareness%20of%20Ng's%20case%2C%20it%20certainly%20hasn't%20hit%20the%20headlines%20to%20the%20extent%20Petito's%20disappearance%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20on%20TikTok%20with%20the%20hashtag%20%23GabbyPetito%20also%20amassed%202.2%20billion%20views%20%E2%80%94%2061%20times%20more%20than%20those%20tagged%20with%20%23NancyNg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikToker%20and%20musician%20Arigato%20Grande%20addressed%20this%20issue%20and%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Binfuriated%26quot%3B%20with%20how%20Ng's%20case%20had%20been%20handled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvm.tiktok.com%2FZGeRCFvY5%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20November%204%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20the%20witnesses%20staying%20silent%2C%20to%20two%20weeks%20of%20minimal%20media%20coverage%2C%20to%20the%20Guatemalan%20navy%20giving%20up%20their%20search%20in%2072%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20cared%20so%20much%20about%20Gabby%20Petito's%20case%2C%20you%20need%20to%20also%20care%20about%20Nancy%20Ng%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20there's%20a%20lot%20going%20on%20in%20the%20world%20right%20now%2C%20but%20our%20friend%20is%20missing%20and%20the%20family%20is%20suffering.%20They%20need%20answers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-sleuths-obsessing-over-case-of-nancy-ng-who-vanished-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701697359000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656db1987a3c8094d5d91280%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-sleuths-obsessing-over-case-of-nancy-ng-who-vanished-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nancy%20Ng%20went%20missing%20on%20October%2019%20while%20kayaking%20on%20Lake%20Atitl%C3%A1n.%20While%20authorities%20think%20she%20may%20have%20drowned%2C%20her%20family%20and%20friends%20think%20differently%2C%20and%20TikTok%20is%20sharing%20every%20update.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-sleuths-obsessing-over-case-of-nancy-ng-who-vanished-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'BJP%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20retain%20power%20at%20Centre%20if%20...%20'%3A%20Mamata%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A170169715