be%20held%20on%20January%206%20at%20the%20Jakarta%20International%20Stadium%20in%20Indonesia.%20The%20nominations%20for%20various%20categories%2C%20including%20Best%20Digital%20Song%2C%20Best%20Album%2C%20and%20Rookie%20Artist%20of%20the%20Year%2C%20were%20announced%20today.%20BTS%20stars%20Jungkook%20and%20Jimin%20received%20nominations%20for%20Best%20Digital%20Song%2C%20and%20Jungkook%20also%20received%20a%20nomination%20for%20Best%20Album.%20The%20Awards%20will%20be%20hosted%20by%20ASTRO%E2%80%99s%20Cha%20Eun%20Woo%20and%20Sung%20Si%20Kyung.%20Check%20out%20the%20full%20list%20of%20nominations%20below.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2F38th-golden-disc-awards-btss-jungkook-jimin-jisoo-compete-for-best-digital-song-check-out-complete-list-of-nominations%2Farticleshow%2F105731716.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Aware%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20To%20Skip%20Next%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20will%20not%20attend%20the%20next%20INDIA%20alliance%20coordination%20meeting%20on%20Wednesday.%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20said%20the%20Congress%20lost%20the%20recent%20state%20elections%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20with%20other%20INDIA%20members%2C%20has%20a%20pre-scheduled%20programme%20in%20north%20Bengal%20on%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20aware%20about%20this%20(the%20meeting)%20and%20I%20have%20some%20programs%20scheduled%20for%20north%20Bengal%2C%20if%20I%20had%20information%20about%20this%20then%20I%20would%20not%20have%20gone%20to%20north%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20party%20Trinamool%20Congress%20may%20also%20skip%20the%20meeting%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20yesterday%20called%20for%20the%20next%20meeting%20of%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20even%20as%20it%20was%20handed%20big%20defeats%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20three%20states.%20The%20meeting%20is%20being%20held%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20three%20months%20since%20the%20last%20one%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20August%2031%20and%20September%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20is%20expected%20to%20chalk%20out%20plans%20for%20next%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20swept%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20handing%20a%20shattering%20defeat%20to%20the%20Congress%20to%20tighten%20its%20stranglehold%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20proverbial%20silver%20lining%20for%20the%20Congress%20was%20Telangana%20where%20it%20ousted%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%20-%20billed%20by%20many%20as%20a%20semi-final%20before%20next%20year's%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20put%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20in%20a%20state%20of%20limbo%20as%20it%20focused%20on%20the%20state%20elections%2C%20received%20flak%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20allies%20who%20blamed%20the%20party's%20decision%20not%20to%20fight%20the%20elections%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20said%20the%20Congress%20decision%20to%20fight%20the%20polls%20on%20its%C2%A0%20led%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bdivision%20of%20votes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20won%20Telangana.%20They%20would%20have%20won%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Some%20votes%20were%20cut%20by%20INDIA%20parties.%20This%20is%20the%20truth.%20We%20had%20said%20suggested%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement.%20They%20lost%20because%20of%20division%20of%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%20in%20an%20address%20to%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20National%20General%20Secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20attempt%20to%20bring%20everyone%20together%20should%20gain%20momentum.%20It%20should%20be%20reflected%20in%20the%20actions%20and%20not%20in%20their%20words.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20everybody%20is%20fighting%20unitedly%20against%20the%20autocratic%20BJP.%20Not%20much%20time%20is%20left%20and%20hence%2C%20we%20should%20utilise%20the%20time%20which%20is%20left.%20Ignoring%20the%20self-interests%2C%20we%20need%20to%20work%20for%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people.%20Keeping%20aside%20the%20political%20ego%2C%20people%20who%20are%20strong%20and%20competent%20in%20their%20regions%20should%20be%20given%20the%20chance%20to%20fight.%20This%20will%20benefit%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Omar%20Abdullah%20taunted%20the%20Congress%20for%20belatedly%20remembering%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%3A%20%26quot%3BOn%20December%206%2C%20the%20Congress%20chief%20has%20invited%20some%20INDIA%20alliance%20leaders%20for%20lunch.%20They%20recalled%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20after%20three%20months.%20Let's%20see%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20drubbing%2C%20said%20it%20would%20introspect%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20two%20states%20it%20held%20-%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20-%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%2C%20according%20to%20the%20sources%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMistakes%20have%20taken%20place%20and%20we%20will%20make%20course%20corrections%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BOver%20confidence%20in%20some%20states%20and%20refusal%20to%20adhere%20to%20proper%20candidates%20and%20campaign%20cost%20us%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20of%20the%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20however%2C%20asserted%20that%20the%20results%20will%20not%20impact%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20stressing%20the%20bloc%20needs%20to%20work%20harder%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVictories%20and%20losses%20happen.%20We%20should%20learn%20from%20the%20defeat%2C%20as%20well%20as%20from%20those%20who%20have%20won.%20India%20has%20to%20be%20one%2C%20it%20is%20for%20everyone%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20strengthen%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%20leader%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BINDIA%20has%20to%20get%20back%20where%20we%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20%26quot%3BWe%20started%20on%20the%20point%20that%20we%20have%20to%20support%20the%20parties%20in%20the%20regions%20they%20are%20strong%20in.%20The%202024%20polls%20will%20be%20historic.%20There%20will%20be%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701695880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Frfjlo1lk_sonia-gandhi-mamata-banerjee_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-trinamool-may-skip-next-india-bloc-meet-not-aware-4632798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20will%20not%20attend%20the%20next%20INDIA%20alliance%20coordination%20meeting%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-trinamool-may-skip-next-india-bloc-meet-not-aware-4632798%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-trinamool-may-skip-next-india-bloc-meet-not-aware-4632798%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-trinamool-may-skip-next-india-bloc-meet-not-aware-4632798%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-US%20ambassador%20arrested%20for%20serving%20as%20an%20agent%20of%20Cuba%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22