20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20euphoria%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20definitely%20examine%20the%20election%20results%20with%20a%20cool%20head.%20The%20election%20results%20may%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20endorsement%20of%20the%20style%20of%20governance%20adopted%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20Delhi%20and%20in%20the%20states%20ruled%20by%20the%20party.%20It%20will%20be%20tempted%20to%20do%20more%20of%20the%20same%20thing%20instead%20of%20tweaking%20its%20style%20ahead%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20delve%20into%20whether%20the%20BJP%20scored%20a%20stupendous%20victory%20in%20three%20states%20because%20of%20its%20style%20of%20governance%20or%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20a%20strong%20and%20trustworthy%20leader.%20The%20Modi%20factor%20and%20overall%20governance%20are%20different%2C%20though%20they%20may%20seem%20like%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin.%20The%20distinction%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20is%2C%20Modi%20dominated%20the%20state%20election%20like%20a%20colossus.%20Efforts%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20puncture%20the%20goodwill%20towards%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20did%20not%20yield%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20is%20more%20than%20a%20leader.%20He%20is%20a%20factor%20competing%20with%20other%20election-related%20issues%20like%20the%20influence%20of%20caste%20and%20the%20people's%20satisfaction%20or%20dissatisfaction%20with%20local%20governments.%20The%20BJP%20won%20in%20Rajasthan%20as%20the%20incumbency%20factor%20restricted%20the%20Congress%2C%20while%20it%20gained%20ground%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20despite%20anti-incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20won%20elections%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades%20until%20her%20assassination%20in%201984%20due%20to%20something%20described%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BIndira%20factor%26quot%3B.%20Ardent%20believers%20even%20called%20it%20the%20%26quot%3BDurga%20syndrome%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongressmen%20under%20her%20were%20corrupt%20and%20arrogant.%20This%20did%20not%20affect%20her%20popularity%20or%20diminish%20her%20magnetism.%20Congress%20leaders%20fawned%20over%20her%20as%20Gandhi%20rose%20to%20become%20the%20primary%20vote-getter%2C%20rendering%20many%20leading%20politicians%20useless%20at%20the%20hustings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20in%20a%20similar%20position%20today%20with%20Modi%20as%20the%20primary%20vote-getter.%20Though%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20has%20built%20some%20kind%20of%20mini-cult%20among%20a%20section%20of%20people%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20has%20a%20strong%20following%20of%20his%20own%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20are%20satellites%20of%20planet%20Modi.%20Yogi%20and%20Chouhan%20would%20be%20powerless%20without%20the%20Modi%20factor%20backing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20latest%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20need%20props%20like%20the%20Ram%20temple%20issue%20or%20the%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20debate%2C%20as%20long%20as%20Modi%20is%20available%20to%20make%20whirlwind%20campaign%20tours%20in%202024.%20This%20one%20factor%20is%20enough.%20The%20election%20results%20are%20a%20confirmation%20that%20this%20factor%20continues%20to%20hold%20sway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20time%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20his%20government%20should%20raise%20their%20attention%20on%20governance%20and%20improve%20the%20delivery%20of%20welfare%20schemes.%20Many%20issues%20are%20crying%20for%20attention.%20The%20lack%20of%20sufficient%20doctors%20and%20medical%20equipment%20in%20rural%20areas%20is%20one%20such.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20crisis%20when%2041%20workers%20were%20trapped%20in%20a%20highway%20construction%20tunnel%20for%2017%20days%20is%20an%20example.%20The%20episode%20raised%20serious%20questions%2C%20not%20just%20about%20the%20design%20and%20construction%20work%20but%20also%20about%20how%20the%20government%20and%20supervisory%20agencies%20had%20allowed%20such%20lopsided%20construction%20without%20an%20escape%20route%20for%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnel%20crisis%20shows%20that%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20particularly%20those%20involved%20in%20supervising%20government%20projects%2C%20have%20a%20mind%20of%20their%20own.%20These%20self-serving%20officials%20need%20to%20be%20identified%20and%20punished%20before%20another%20breaks%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20factor%20supersedes%20all%20other%20issues%20in%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20belt%20barring%20Bihar%2C%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20tested.%20Most%20of%20the%20BJP's%20issue-based%20campaigns%2C%20like%20the%20temple%20issue%2C%20are%20focused%20on%20the%20Hindi%20belt.%20These%20campaigns%20may%20not%20be%20required.%20Instead%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20should%20be%20seen%20by%20the%20public%20as%20directing%20welfare%20schemes%20by%20physically%20being%20present%20at%20the%20points%20of%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%2C%20which%20sent%20ministers%20and%20MPs%20to%20different%20states%20to%20campaign%20for%20elections%2C%20should%20now%20ask%20them%20to%20closely%20monitor%20and%20supervise%20the%20implementation%20of%20projects%20and%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20results%20have%20spurred%20an%20important%20question%3A%20are%20freebies%20enough%20to%20sway%20voters%20against%20something%20like%20the%20Modi%20factor%3F%20The%20freebies%20offered%20by%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20did%20not%20stop%20the%20Congress%20from%20losing%20a%20large%20number%20of%20seats%20it%20was%20holding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFreebies%20like%20the%20popular%20cheap%20rice%20distribution%20schemes%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20refashioned%20to%20meet%20urban%20needs%20by%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20have%20now%20come%20to%20stay.%20Politicians%20of%20all%20parties%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20offer%20it%20not%20merely%20to%20sway%20voters%20but%20to%20stay%20in%20competition%20with%20rival%20parties%20making%20tall%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20question%20still%20remains%20about%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20it%20is%20useful%20in%20a%20scenario%20where%20all%20parties%20offer%20more%20of%20the%20same.%20Being%20a%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20the%20BJP%20needs%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20strain%20that%20freebies%20will%20impose%20on%20the%20national%20exchequer%20and%20how%20it%20would%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20funds%20needed%20for%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20other%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20leader%20who%20is%20admired%20at%20home%20and%20abroad%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20reasons%20to%20be%20concerned%20about%20his%20legacy%20as%20an%20effective%20administrator%20and%20statesman%2C%20which%20is%20much%20weightier%20than%20the%20image%20of%20an%20election%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20the%20BJP%20should%20use%20the%20opportunity%20offered%20by%20the%20election%20results%20and%20the%20confirmation%20of%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Modi%20image%20to%20concentrate%20on%20performance%20and%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Saibal%20Dasgupta%20is%20a%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20and%20China%20expert)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701695700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fphdednj8_modi-ani_625x300_04_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-modi-factor-overrides-all-campaign-issues-4633205%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20neighbour%2C%20a%20senior%20engineer%2C%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20the%20special%20blessings%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20and%20he%20would%20not%20stop%20until%20he%20has%20destroyed%20the%20Opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F