%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20neigbhbours%20heard%20her%20screaming%2C%20they%20called%20the%20cops%20who%20found%20Ms%20Skoland%20being%20mauled%20by%20the%20dogs.%20They%20initially%20attempted%20to%20scare%20the%20dogs%20away%20with%20pepper%20spray%C2%A0but%20were%20forced%20to%20shoot%20each%20dog%20multiple%20times%2C%20killing%20all%20three.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20officer%20attempted%20to%20scare%20the%20dogs%20away%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20attacking%20the%20woman%2C%20but%20the%20dogs%20would%20not%20stop.%20The%20officer%20on%20scene%20then%20drew%20his%20duty%20weapon%20and%20shot%20all%20three%20dogs%20multiple%20times%20to%20stop%20the%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20Police%20Chief%20Dennis%20Quinn%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20department's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%2F%3Ffbid%3D743565631139880%26set%3Da.228376272658821%5C%22%3EFacebook%20page.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252FFortDodgePoliceDepartmentOfficial%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0sUKDFYjF73py7K5f8wbbo8vGm21GZE1JLkcAoicbi4SpfMbm2UBWoY9Z4S47dqjel%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20left%20her%20in%20a%20critical%20condition%20and%20she%20was%20rushed%20to%20Unity%20Point%20Trinity%20Medical%20Center%20before%20being%20airlifted%20to%20Iowa%20Methodist%20Medical%20Center.%20She%20suffered%20severe%20head%20trauma%20and%20underwent%20several%20surgeries.%20She%20had%20both%20legs%20amputated%20to%20her%20knees%20and%20also%20lost%20parts%20of%20her%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''This%20is%20a%20tragic%20situation%20involving%20a%20mother%20and%20her%20son's%20dogs%20in%20the%20backyard%20of%20their%20home.%20Our%20hearts%20are%20heavy%20following%20this%20incident%2C%20and%20we%20are%20grateful%20the%20victim%20was%20able%20to%20call%20911%20for%20help%20as%20quickly%20as%20she%20did%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20the%20attack%20was%20happening.%20It%20likely%20did%20save%20her%20life%2C''%20said%20Police%20Chief%20Brady%20Cottam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20neighbour%20Rosemary%20Possehn%20who%20saw%20the%20events%20unfold%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kcci.com%2Farticle%2Fiowa-fort-dodge-woman-recovering-in-hospital-after-dog-attack%2F45965357%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKCCI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20was%20sitting%20in%20my%20living%20room%2C%20and%20I%20was%20just%20sitting%20there%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20I%20heard%20bang%2C%20bang%2C%20bang%2C%20and%20I%20come%20to%20the%20door%20and%20I%20saw%20all%20the%20cops%2C%20well%20there%20was%20only%20one%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20I%20seen%20the%20lady%20laying%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20the%20dogs%20going%20at%20her%20and%20the%20cops%20shot%20them.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fajyez6-attacked-by-dogs%3F%5C%22%3EGoFundMe%20page%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20help%20pay%20for%20Ms%20Skoland's%20medical%20bills%2C%20her%20aunt%20Teresa%20Hanus%20wrote%2C%20''As%20of%2012%2F2%20Brittany%20has%20lost%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20we%20originally%20thought.%20She's%20had%20many%20surgeries%20and%20procedures%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days.%20She%20has%20had%20both%20legs%20amputated%20to%20her%20knees.%20Brittany%20did%20not%20need%20surgery%20on%20her%20hands%20as%20we%20had%20originally%20thought.%20However%20she%20is%20going%20to%20need%20facial%20reconstruction%20surgery%2C%20she%20also%20has%20serious%20head%20trauma%20and%20much%20more.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Those%20who%20know%20Brittany%2C%20know%20she%20loves%20to%20be%20outside%2C%20doing%20yard%20work%2C%20helping%20her%20Mom%20decorate%20for%20the%20Holid