20only%20four%20from%20Bastar%20and%20none%20in%20Sarguja.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20BJP%20won%2017%20of%20the%2029%20seats%20reserved%20for%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20category.%20The%20party%20has%20won%2054%20of%20the%20state's%2090%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20got%20only%2035%2C%20down%20from%20the%2068%20they%20bagged%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20dismal%20performance%20in%20tribal%20areas%2C%20Mr%20Deo%20said%20the%20margins%20of%20BJP%20victory%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20tribal%20votes%20%26quot%3Bhaven't%20shifted%20away%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20seat%20we%20lost%20by%2014%20votes%2C%20one%20by%20100%20to%20200%20votes%2C%20another%20by%2094.%20The%20margins%20are%20not%20too%20much.%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20has%20been%20a%20shift%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%20The%20BJP%2C%20he%20contended%2C%20had%20drawn%20up%20a%20better%20programme%20for%20women%20which%20has%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20tribals%20have%20been%20unhappy%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years%20has%20been%20clear%20by%20the%20volume%20of%20protests%20over%20the%20price%20of%20tendu%20leaves%20and%20other%20minor%20forest%20products.%20Tendu%20leaves%20or%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20gold%26quot%3B%20are%20the%20biggest%20source%20of%20income%20for%20tribals%2C%20who%20finally%20took%20it%20to%20the%20open%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202021%2C%20four%20persons%20died%20in%20police%20firing%20during%20a%20protest%20in%20Sukma%20district%2C%2046%20people%20were%20injured%2C%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20died%20in%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20backlash%20came%20now.%20As%20after%20the%20farmers'%20death%20in%20Mandsaur%20police%20firing%2C%20the%20farmer%20vote%20swung%20towards%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20tribals%20turned%20to%20the%20BJP%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20also%20helped%20was%20the%20BJP's%20grassroot%20campaign%2C%20which%20pen