%20fortresses%20that%20can%20target%20any%20threat%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20and%20rain%20death%20and%20destruction%20upon%20the%20world%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20%E2%80%98the%20international%20community%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELong%20before%20the%20Captain%20America%20character%20learns%20that%20the%20programme%20has%20been%20infiltrated%20and%20taken%20over%20by%20an%20evil%20organisation%20(Hydra)%2C%20he%20opposes%20this%20project%2C%20asking%20what%20happened%20to%20innocent%20until%20proven%20guilty%2C%20stating%20bluntly%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20hold%20a%20gun%20on%20everyone%20on%20Earth%20and%20call%20it%20protection.%20This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20freedom.%20This%20is%20fear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20later%20scene%2C%20interrogating%20one%20of%20the%20Hydra%20members%20that%20will%20use%20the%20hellicarriers%20for%20their%20own%20purposes%2C%20Captain%20America%20and%20his%20friends%20learn%20that%20the%20vehicles%20will%20be%20implanted%20with%20an%20algorithm%20that%20will%20erase%20potentially%20problematic%20people%20%E2%80%9Ca%20million%20at%20a%20time%E2%80%9D.%20The%20algorithm%20will%20process%20enormous%20data%20from%20social%20media%20feeds%20and%20public%20information%20to%20determine%20who%20these%20problematic%20people%20were.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20say%20that%20life%20sometimes%20imitates%20art%2C%20although%20rarely%20as%20neatly.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20months%20as%20Israel%20has%20rained%20death%20and%20destruction%20on%20Gaza%2C%20one%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fmass-assassination-factory-israel-calculated-bombing-gaza%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ekey%20enablers%20of%20the%20destruction%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20widespread%20use%20of%20a%20system%20called%20%E2%80%98Habsora%E2%80%99%20(%E2%80%98The%20Gospel%E2%80%99)%2C%20which%20is%20largely%20built%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20can%20%E2%80%98generate%E2%80%99%20targets%20almost%20automatically%20at%20a%20rate%20that%20far%20exceeds%20what%20was%20previously%20possible.%E2%80%9D%20The%20investigation%20by%20the%20publications%20%3Cem%3E%2B972%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Local%20Call%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20relying%20on%20a%20series%20of%20interviews%20with%20Israeli%20intelligence%20and%20military%20people%2C%20highlights%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20use%20of%20a%20system%20like%20Habsora%20makes%20it%20possible%20to%20locate%20and%20attack%20the%20homes%20of%20relatively%20junior%20operatives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04161356%2FScreenshot-2023-12-04-at-4.12.21-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04161356%2FScreenshot-2023-12-04-at-4.12.21-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04161356%2FScreenshot-2023-12-04-at-4.12.21-PM-300x125.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04161356%2FScreenshot-2023-12-04-at-4.12.21-PM-1024x428.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687646%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22501%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHellicarriers%20in%20the%20film.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBear%20in%20mind%20what%20this%20means.%20These%20are%20not%20the%20planners%20of%20the%20attacks%2C%20and%20since%20the%20system%20relies%20on%20association%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20evidence%20that%20any%20of%20these%20%E2%80%9Cjunior%20operatives%E2%80%9D%20took%20part%20in%20the%20horrific%20attacks%20on%20civilians%20on%20October%207%2C%20or%20any%20violent%20action%20ever.%20Instead%2C%20such%20murders%20are%20based%20on%20guilt%20by%20association%2C%20and%20because%20they%20are%20attacks%20on%20homes%2C%20also%20on%20the%20families%20of%20these%20people%20as%20well%20as%20anybody%20living%20in%20the%20same%20building.%20Worse%2C%20of%20course%2C%20are%20the%20attacks%20on%20what%20the%20Israeli%20military%20classifies%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpower%20targets%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20are%20mainly%20civilian%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%93%20high-rise%20buildings%2C%20banks%2C%20even%20post%20offices%20%E2%80%93%20so%20civilians%20put%20pressure%20on%20Hamas.%20In%20legal%20terms%2C%20this%20is%20what%20is%20known%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasebook.icrc.org%2Fa_to_z%2Fglossary%2Fcollective-punishments%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecollective%20punishment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fwhy-all-civilian-lives-matter-equally-according-to-a-military-ethicist-218686%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeliberate%20targeting%20of%20non-combatants%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20war%20crimes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20will%20not%20be%20difficult%20for%20pro-Palestinian%20groups%20to%20draw%20a%20straight%20line%20with%20the%20helicarriers%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Winter%20Soldier%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20governing%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20as%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fnews%2F2022%2F06%2F14%2Fgaza-israels-open-air-prison-15%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98open-air%20prison%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20And%20it%20will%20be%20even%20easier%20to%20compare%20the%20Hydra%20algorithm%20and%20Habsora%2C%20with%20the%20added%20horror%20of%20the%20many%2C%20many%20civilian%20casualties%20of%20the%20attacks%20on%20%E2%80%9Cpower%20targets%E2%80%9D.%20But%20where%20is%20Captain%20America%20in%20all