3C%2Fem%3E.%20Recently%2C%20Goa%20State%20Commissioner%20for%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20ordered%20two%20district%20administrations%20to%20stop%20the%20movie%20from%20screening.%20The%20office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Commissioner%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20also%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20movie%20and%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Film%20Certification%20seeking%20a%20response%20from%20them%2C%20as%20the%20movie%20violated%20Sections%203%20(non-discrimination)%20and%2092%20(punishment%20for%20offences%20of%20atrocities)%20of%20the%20Rights%20of%20Person%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%2C%202016%20(RPwD%20Act).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20brief%2C%20the%20story%20is%20based%20on%20a%20family%20of%20six.%20Barring%20two%20members%2C%20all%20of%20them%20live%20with%20some%20form%20of%20disability.%20%C2%A0The%20story%20is%20premised%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20the%20marriage%20of%20the%20lead%20character%20(Mrunal%20Thakur)%2C%20who%20is%20living%20with%20a%20visual%20disability%2C%20rendering%20her%20unable%20to%20see%20at%20night.%20The%20underlying%20premise%20is%20that%20the%20disability%20is%20a%20disease%20that%20has%20to%20be%20hidden%20from%20outsiders%20(including%20the%20one%20you%20will%20be%20marrying).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUndoing%20the%20understanding%20of%20disability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disability%20movement%20across%20generations%20has%20struggled%20to%20eradicate%20the%20engrained%20idea%20of%20the%20medical%20model%20of%20disability%2C%20wherein%20your%20disability%20is%20identified%20in%20the%20medical%20condition.%20The%20American%20civil%20rights%20movement%20percolated%20into%20the%20disability%20rights%20movement.%20Thus%2C%20the%20social%20model%20of%20disability%20was%20followed%2C%20wherein%20societal%20barriers%20are%20identified%20as%20the%20source%20of%20disability%20and%20not%20the%20individual.%20This%20understanding%20was%20implemented%20through%20legislative%20mandate%20under%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%2C%202016%2C%20which%20used%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cperson%20with%20disability%E2%80%9D%20rather%20than%20a%20disabled%20person%20%E2%80%93%20placing%20individuals%20at%20the%20forefront.%20It%20also%20defines%20a%20person%20with%20disability%20in%20a%20more%20social%20sense%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ea%20person%20with%20long-term%20physical%2C%20mental%2C%20intellectual%20or%20sensory%20impairment%20which%2C%20in%20%3Cstrong%3Einteraction%20with%20barriers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20hinders%20his%20full%20and%20effective%20participation%20in%20society%20equally%20with%20others%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20makers%20of%20this%20movie%20and%20others%20in%20the%20Indian%20cinema%20world%20have%20systematically%20misconstrued%20this%20fundamental%20differentiation.%20In%20the%20movie%2C%20characters%20often%20view%20the%20inherent%20disability%20as%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20characteristic%20and%20a%20painful%20extra.%20Disability%20is%20termed%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebeemari%3C%2Fem%3E%20(disease).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20legal%20excuse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apparent%20argument%20from%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20movie%20is%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20creative%20liberty.%20This%20overarching%20freedom%20is%20also%20limited%20by%20reasonable%20limitation%20under%20Article%2019(2)%2C%20specifically%20decency%20and%20morality.%20The%20makers%20have%20rendered%20the%20creation%20an%20ideal%20piece%20of%20ableism%20devoid%20of%20decency.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20proactively%20decided%20not%20to%20confine%20the%20contours%20of%20decency%20to%20just%20acts%20of%20a%20sexual%20nature%20but%20has%20widened%20the%20horizons%20to%20include%20acts%20that%20would%20invite%20a%20collective%20shock%2C%20disgust%20or%20revolt.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F925631%2F%5C%22%3EDr.%20Ramesh%20Yeshwant%20Prabhoo%20vs%20Shri%20Prabhakar%20Kashinath%20Kunte%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20explaining%20indecency%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3EIndecency%20is%20not%20confined%20to%20sexual%20indecency%3B%20indeed%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20find%20any%20limit%20short%20of%20saying%20that%20it%20includes%20anything%20which%20an%20ordinary%20decent%20man%20or%20woman%20would%20find%20to%20be%20shocking%2C%20disgusting%20and%20revolting%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20makers%20in%20the%20work%20employ%20the%20ableist%20framework%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20screenplay%2C%20garbed%20as%20humour.%20This%20fundamentally%20invites%20disgust%20from%20a%20large%20sect%20of%20society%20whose%20lives%20are%20depicted%20as%20devoid%20of%20any%20dignity.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fjournal%2Fsco-explains-vikash-kumar-v-upsc%2F%5C%22%3EVikash%20Kumar%20vs%20UPSC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20explaining%20the%20dignity%20of%20persons%20with%20disabilities%2C%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cintrinsic%20to%20individual%20dignity.%20is%20recognising%20the%20worth%20of%20every%20person%20as%20an%20equal%20member%20of%20the%20society%2C%20respect%20for%20the%20dignity%20of%20others%20and%20fostering%20conditions%20in%20which%20every%20individual%20can%20evolve%20according%20to%20his%20capabilities%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98Sam%20Bahadur%E2%80%99%3A%20Yet%20Another%20Biopic%20That%20Is%20in%20Awe%20of%20Its%20Protagonist%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fsam-bahadur-biopic-review-meghan-gulzar-vicky-kaushal%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Sam%20Bahadur%E2%80%99%3A%20Yet%20Another%20Biopic%20That%20Is%20in%20Awe%20of%20Its%20Protagonist%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%205B%20of%20the%20Cinematograph%20Act%2C%201952%20deals%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Principles%20of%20guidance%20in%20certifying%20films%E2%80%99.%20Subsection%20(1)%20of%20section%205B%20allows%20the%20film%20certification%20authorities%20to%20not%20certify%20a%20film%20for%20public%20exhibition%20if%20it%20is%20against%20%E2%80%9Cdecency%20and%20morality%E2%80%9D.%20This%20can%20serve%20as%20an%20instrument%20to%20direct%20makers%20to%20comply%20with%20basic%20tenets%20of%20dignity%20wherein%20creativity%20subordinates%20every%20other%20aspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RPwD%20Act%20was%20implemented%20to%20ensure%20equality%20and%20dignity%20for%20persons%20with%20disabilities.%20Resultantly%2C%20section%203%20of%20the%20RPwD%20Act%20talks%20about%20equality%20and%20non-discrimination.%20It%20is%20operationalised%20in%20different%20sectors%20through%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20RPwD%20Act%2C%20wherein%20government%20and%20private%20bodies%20are%20obligated%20to%20ensure%20this%20mandate.%20%C2%A0Thus%2C%20the%20Cinematograph%20Act%20must%20be%20aligned%20with%20these%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreating%20stereotype%20through%20cinema%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phenomenon%20is%20not%20new%20and%20is%20documented%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstanford.edu%2F~kartiks2%2FdisabilityInBollywood.pdf%5C%22%3Eseminal%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Joyojeet%20Pal.%20He%20underlines%20four%20trends%20in%20Indian%20films%3A%20first%2C%20disability%20as%20punitive%3B%20second%2C%20disability%20as%20dependence%3B%20third%2C%20disability%20as%20disequilibrium%20and%20fourth%2C%20disability%20as%20maladjustment.%20For%20the%20first%20trend%2C%20an%20all-time%20classic%20%3Cem%3ESholay%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1975)%20fits%20the%20mould%3B%20the%20antagonist%20thinks%20chopping%20off%20a%20character%E2%80%99s%20arms%20is%20worse%20than%20death.%20Disability%20as%20a%20divine%20punishment%20has%20also%20been%20a%20central%20theme%20for%20makers%2C%20which%20is%20visible%20in%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3EDhanwaan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(1981).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20aspect%2C%20and%20probably%20the%20most%20prominent%20one%2C%20is%20of%20disability%20as%20dependence.%20The%20sympathetic%20attitude%20towards%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20is%20often%20transformed%20into%20the%20object%20of%20pity%20and%20a%20metaphor%20depicting%20helplessness.%20This%20is%20catalysed%20by%20cinematic%20depiction.%20Pal%2C%20in%20his%20paper%2C%20underscores%20a%20series%20of%20films%20that%20have%20regularly%20employed%20this%20trend%2C%20mainly%20as%20a%20subject%20of%20violence%20because%20of%20this%20dependence%2C%20like%20in%20%3Cem%3EHum%20Aapko%20Aapse%20Pyaar%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2006)%20or%20an%20all-time%20classic%20like%20%3Cem%3EMother%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(1957)%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20wherein%20the%20disability%20is%20looked%20at%20with%20ridicule%20as%20it%20is%20presumed%20to%20default%20dependence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20and%20fourth%20aspects%20are%20closely%20related%20to%20finding%20disability%20as%20something%20extra%20that%20burdens%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20live%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnormal%E2%80%9D%20life%20in%20a%20society.%20This%20is%20evidenced%20in%20the%20screenplays%20where%20the%20protagonist%E2%80%99s%20sole%20objective%20is%20to%20either%20correct%20her%2Fhis%20disability%20or%20that%20of%20someone%20else.%20This%20is%20vividly%20visible%20in%20Shatrughan%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20movie%20%3Cem%3EAa%20Gale%20Lag%20Jaa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1974)%2C%20where%20he%20endeavours%20to%20cure%20a%20polio-struck%20boy%20by%20employing%20the%20most%20extreme%20form%20of%20mental%20violence.%20Thus%2C%20as%20Pal%20mentions%20in%20his%20paper%2C%20there%20is%20a%20dearth%20of%20cinema%20wherein%20the%20protagonist%20stays%20disabled%20throughout%20the%20film.%20Recent%20creations%20like%20%3Cem%3EMargarita%20with%20a%20Straw%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2014)%20or%20%3Cem%3EGuzaarish%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(2010)%20serve%20as%20an%20exception%20on%20this%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Animal%3A%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%E2%80%99s%20Crude%20and%20Beastly%20Assault%20on%20Sense%20and%20Sensibility%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fanimal-sandeep-reddy-vangas-crude-and-beastly-assault-on-sense-and-sensibility%5C%22%3EAnimal%3A%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%E2%80%99s%20Crude%20and%20Beastly%20Assault%20on%20Sense%20and%20Sensibility%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20maladjustment%20aspect%20of%20disability%20further%20attributes%20the%20trait%20of%20evilness.%20This%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Freel%2F1007109%2Fwhy-a-disfigured-or-disabled-screen-villain-is-an-idea-that-needs-to-die%5C%22%3Enot%20unique%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Indian%20films%2C%20as%20the%20recent%20addition%20to%20James%20Bond%E2%80%99s%20franchise%20showed%20Rame%20Malek%20as%20having%20a%20disability%20to%20underline%20his%20evil%20characters%20further.%20However%2C%20the%20most%20common%20usage%C2%A0%20of%20this%20aspect%20in%20in%20comedy%2C%20which%20is%20exactly%20what%20makers%20of%3Cem%3E%20Aankh%20Micholi%3C%2Fem%3E%20intended%20to%20do.%20A%20few%20examples%20include%20%3Cem%3EHum%20Hai%20Kamaal%20ke%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1993)%20or%20%3Cem%3ETom%20Dick%20and%20Harry%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2006)%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20makers%20of%20%3Cem%3EAankh%20Micholi%3C%2Fem%3E%20indulge%20in%20establishing%20the%20undertone%20that%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20are%20not%20necessarily%20equal%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20have%20to%20fit%20into%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage.%20The%20underlying%20messaging%20%C2%A0of%20the%20film%20%E2%80%93%20that%20to%20fit%20in%20the%20most%20fundamental%20unit%20of%20our%20society%2C%20people%20with%20disabilities%20must%20hide%20their%20disability%20%E2%80%93%20cannot%20be%20overlooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERespect%20the%20new%20reality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindi%20cinema%20has%20seen%20a%20transition%20to%20accommodate%20disability%20more%20meaningfully%20and%20is%20sticking%20to%20a%20new%20understanding%20of%20the%20concept.%20This%20understanding%20is%20depicted%20in%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3EBlack%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2005)%20and%20%3Cem%3EMy%20Name%20is%20Khan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(2010).%20The%20makers%20don%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20have%20to%20overwrite%20disability%20in%20their%20screenplay%20for%20any%20of%20the%20four%20trends%20mentioned%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Bollywood%20wants%20to%20make%20a%20comedy%20using%20disability%20as%20the%20central%20theme%2C%20they%20might%20wish%20to%20experiment%20with%20an%20extreme%20option%3A%20casting%20a%20person%20with%20a%20disability.%20In%20the%20movies%20%3Cem%3EPeanut%20Butter%20Falcon%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2019)%20or%20%3Cem%3EGive%20me%20Liberty%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2019)%2C%20an%20actor%20with%20Down%20Syndrome%20and%20locomotor%20disability%20shows%20that%20comedic%20timing%20is%20not%20the%20exclusive%20domain%20of%20able-bodied%20individuals%20but%20rather%20a%20skill%20to%20be%20acquired%20with%20effort.%20It%20might%20not%20have%20to%20look%20far%20for%20inspiration%20either.%20Gulzar%E2%80%99s%201972%20classic%20%3Cem%3EKoshish%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20its%20poster%20and%20introduction%20credits%20in%20sign%20language%2C%20as%20the%20lead%20actors%20were%20living%20with%20some%20form%20of%20disability.%20The%20character%20depicted%20that%20they%20can%20live%20independently%20if%20society%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20interfere.%20This%20conceptual%20understanding%20was%20far%20ahead%20in%20both%20cinematic%20and%20political%20discourse.%20The%20decline%20of%20Indian%20cinema%20from%20%3Cem%3EKoshish%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20%3Cem%3EAankh%20Micholi%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20disability%20depiction%20shows%20the%20intellectual%20bankruptcy%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20makers.%20Making%20disability%20a%20joke%20is%20neither%20comedy%20nor%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShashank%20Pandey%20is%20a%20lawyer%20and%20policy%20researcher%20working%20on%20the%20cases%20of%20disability%20issues.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20person%20with%20Low%20Vision%20disability.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701689403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04162855%2Fcap.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmaking-disability-a-joke-is-neither-comedy-nor-art%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20film%20'Aankh%20Micholi'%20portrays%20characters%20with%20disabilities%20as%20having%20a%20problem%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20hidden.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmaking-disability-a-joke-is-neither-comedy-nor-art%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jio%20AirFiber%20unveils%20data%20booster%20plan%20details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701689377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105729040%2Cimgsize-10980.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fjio-airfiber-has-a-data-booster-plan-heres-why-it-does-may-not-be-too-useful%2Farticleshow%2F105729040.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reliance%20Jio%20recently%20introduced%20the%20JioAirFiber%20service%20in%20select%20cities%2C%20offering%20wireless%20broadband%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20plans%20based%20on%20speed%20and%20additional%20benefits.%20One%20such%20plan%20is%20the%20Rs%20401%20data%20booster%20plan%2C%20which%20provides%201TB%20of%20high-speed%20data%20over%20the%20base%20plan.%20Once%20the%201TB%20quota%20is%20reached%2C%20the%20plan%20becomes%20unlimited%20at%20a%20reduced%20speed.%20The%20booster%20plan%20can%20be%20recharged%20multiple%20times%20within%20the%20same%20billing%20cycle%2C%20and%20its%20speed%20depends%20on%20the%20base%20plan%20of%20the%20JioAirFiber%20connection.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20availability%20of%20other%20unlimited%20data%20plans%20with%20higher%20speeds%2C%20the%20Rs%20401%20plan%20may%20not%20be%20necessary%20for%20most%20users.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fjio-airfiber-has-a-data-booster-plan-heres-why-it-does-may-not-be-too-useful%2Farticleshow%2F105729040.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20War%20Two%20bomb%20detonated%20off%20coast%20of%20Denmark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701689281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F15CB7%2Fproduction%2F_131917298_p0gxhjjk.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67613803%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20130kg%20bomb%20got%20caught%20in%20a%20fisherman's%20net%20and%20had%20to%20be%20detonated%20by%20the%20Danish%20Navy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A560%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-europe-67613803%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDefeat%20Of%20Congress%2C%20Not%20The%20People%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20On%20BJP's%203-State%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20defeats%20in%20three%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20have%20given%20way%20to%20rumblings%20inside%20the%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc%2C%20with%20allies%20pointing%20out%20how%20the%20main%20opposition%20party's%20decision%20to%20fight%20the%20polls%20on%20its%20own%20led%20to%20a%20division%20of%20votes%2C%20benefiting%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20lost%20the%20polls%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20with%20other%20INDIA%20members%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20today%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdefeat%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20not%20the%20people%26quot%3B.%20Samajwadi%20Party%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20too%2C%20responded%20to%20the%20Congress%20defeats%2C%20suggesting%20that%20regional%20parties%20must%20lead%20the%20fight%20against%20BJP%20in%20areas%20they%20hold%20sway%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20won%20Telangana.%20They%20would%20have%20won%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Some%20votes%20were%20cut%20by%20INDIA%20parties.%20This%20is%20the%20truth.%20We%20had%20said%20suggested%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement.%20They%20lost%20because%20of%20division%20of%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20said%20in%20an%20address%20to%20the%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlong%20with%20ideology%2C%20you%20need%20to%20have%20a%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%2C%20BJP%20won't%20come%20to%20power%20in%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20she%20said%2C%20will%20work%20together%20and%20rectify%20mistakes%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election%20next%20year.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20learn%20from%20the%20mistakes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20come%20after%20the%20Congress%20suffered%20defeats%20in%20three%20heartland%20states%20-%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20The%20party%20managed%20to%20win%20just%20one%20seat%20in%20Mizoram%20after%20contesting%20all%2040.%20Its%20sole%20consolation%20is%20a%20victory%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20round%20of%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20Congress%20and%20its%20INDIA%20allies%20had%20contested%20separately%20on%20many%20seats.%20This%2C%20many%20have%20pointed%20out%2C%20led%20to%20a%20division%20in%20votes%20and%20benefited%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20talks%20with%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20party%2C%20but%20the%20talks%20fell%20apart%20over%20seat-sharing.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20was%20leading%20Congress's%20campaign%2C%20dismissed%20a%20media%20query%20on%20the%20alliance%20talks%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3Bchoro%20Akhilesh%20Vakhilesh%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20remark%20sealed%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20alliance%20talks.%20%26quot%3BThe%20insulting%20words%20used%20for%20Akhileshji%20by%20Kamal%20Nathji%20is%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20Congress's%20loss.%20The%20Congress%20lost%20because%20of%20those%20undignified%20remarks%2C%26quot%3B%20Samajwadi%20Party%20spokesperson%20Manoj%20Yadav%20Kaka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20election%20results%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20today%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20long%20battle.%20We%20have%20to%20prepare%20a%20lot%20to%20defeat%20a%20party%20like%20BJP.%20We%20have%20to%20fight%20their%20strategies%20with%20discipline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20back%20where%20we%20started%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20started%20on%20the%20point%20that%20we%20have%20to%20support%20the%20parties%20in%20the%20regions%20they%20are%20strong%20in.%20The%202024%20polls%20will%20be%20historic.%20There%20will%20be%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20trends%20pointed%20to%20Congress's%20impending%20defeats%20yesterday%2C%20INDIA%20allies%20had%20started%20criticising%20the%20main%20opposition%20party's%20decision%20not%20to%20fight%20the%20elections%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanata%20Dal-United's%20KC%20Tyagi%20said%20the%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bignored%20other%20INDIA%20parties%2C%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20win%20on%20its%20own%26quot%3B.%20Kerala%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20CPM%20leader%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20said%20that%20it%20was%20necessary%20to%20fight%20together%20while%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20said%20the%20outcome%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20polls%20would%20have%20been%20different%20had%20the%20Congress%20shared%20some%20seats%20with%20other%20constituents%20of%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20leader%20from%20a%20major%20Opposition%20party%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20it%20appeared%20that%20Congress%20was%20waiting%20for%20the%20poll%20results%20for%20greater%20bargaining%20powers%20within%20the%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20no%20meetings%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20a%20long%20time.%20The%20Congress%20did%20not%20want%20to%20meet.%20Perhaps%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%20the%20results%20to%20have%20greater%20bargaining%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20its%20gamble%20not%20paying%20off%2C%20the%20main%20Opposition%20party%20is%20now%20on%20the%20backfoot%20before%20the%20next%20meeting%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20this%20Wednesday.%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20is%20unlikely%20to%20attend%20the%20meeting.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701689220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F30vs2e5_mamata-banerjee-sonia-rahul-gandhi-aug2018_625x300_01_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefeat-of-congress-not-the-people-mamata-banerjee-on-bjps-3-state-win-4632171%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20lost%20key%20assembly%20polls%20in%20three%20states%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20with%20INDIA%20members%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20today%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdefeat%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20not%20the%20people%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefeat-of-congress-not-the-people-mamata-banerjee-on-bjps-3-state-win-4632171%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproj