ning-birth-rates-13022656%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2219%20women%20elected%20to%2090-member%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701687791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105728388%2Cimgsize-1217165.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2F19-women-elected-to-90-member-chhattisgarh-assembly%2Farticleshow%2F105728320.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20the%202018%20polls%2C%2010%20women%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20one%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20one%20each%20from%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20and%20Janata%20Congress%20Chhattisgarh%20(J)%20were%20elected.%20Subsequently%2C%20three%20more%20women%20from%20the%20Congress%20were%20elected%20in%20bypolls%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20to%2016.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2F19-women-elected-to-90-member-chhattisgarh-assembly%2Farticleshow%2F105728320.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20Man%2C%2025%2C%20Fighting%20For%20Life%20After%20Being%20Buried%20Alive%20On%20Beach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Australian%20man%2C%2025-year-old%20Josh%20Taylor%2C%20is%20fighting%20for%20his%20life%20in%20the%20hospital%20after%20being%20buried%20by%20sand%20at%20a%20popular%20beach.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20on%20Bribie%20Island%2C%20north%20of%20Brisbane%2C%20where%20Mr%20Taylor%20fell%20into%20a%20hole%20and%20was%20covered%20in%20sand.%20Paramedics%20and%20an%20RACQ%20Life%20flight%20rescue%20helicopter%20crew%20were%20called%20to%20assist%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20witness%20named%20Nathan%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F7news.com.au%2Fnews%2Fman-fighting-for-life-after-being-buried-alive-in-freak-accident-at-bribie-island-c-12769425%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%207News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Mr%20Taylor%20stumbled%20into%20a%20pit%2C%20which%20had%20been%20dug%20to%20cook%20a%20pig.%20%26quot%3BHe%20stood%20up%20off%20the%20chair%3B%20the%20sand%20had%20given%20away%20a%20little%20bit%20underneath%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20stumbled%20back.%20He'd%20put%20his%20arms%20out%20to%20obviously%20break%20the%20fall%2C%20he's%20continued%20going%20down%20and%20knocked%20sand%20as%20he's%20put%20his%20arms%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20so%20deep%20in%20the%20hole%20that%20you%20could%20not%20see%20him%2C%20his%20feet%20unless%20you%20were%20standing%20on%20top%20of%20the%20hole.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENathan%20shared%20that%20the%20efforts%20to%20extricate%20Mr.%20Taylor%20from%20the%20pit%20were%20immense.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%2015%20fully%20grown%20men%20on%20the%20end%20of%20this%20rope%2C%20and%20he%20still%20would%20not%20budge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20the%20paramedic%20was%20like%2C%20pull%20him%20this%20way%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20suction%20gave%20way%20and%20he%20popped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20praying%20that%20he%20pulls%20through%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENathan%20further%20shared%20that%20he%20was%20leaving%20the%20beach%20when%20a%20group%20of%20men%20ran%20over%20yelling%20for%20help%20to%20rescue%20their%20friend%20from%20under%20the%20sand.%20When%20he%20arrived%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20Mr%20Taylor's%20friends%20and%20family%20were%20desperately%20digging%20to%20free%20him%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Fnational%2Fqueensland%2Fnews%2Fparamedics-treat-man-on-bribie-island-north-of-brisbane%2Fnews-story%2F2ea2bff9d48db90c61f0f07d4d2ed8eb%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENews.com.au%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20realized%20someone%20was%20head%20first%20in%20a%20hole%2C%20and%20I%20was%20just%20digging%2C%20digging%2C%20digging...%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20went%20up%20to%20the%20hole%2C%20I%20couldn't%20even%20see%20his%20foot.%20That's%20how%20deep%20it%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20his%20family%20were%20screaming%20at%20us%2C%20telling%20us%20to%20help%2C%20telling%20us%20to%20get%20a%20rope%20so%20we%20could%20pull%20him%20out.%20It%20was%20pretty%20gruesome%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20minutes%2C%20the%20man%20finally%20burst%20through%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20sand%2C%20but%20the%20force%20of%20being%20pulled%20out%20caused%20him%20further%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20pretty%20gnarly%20when%20he%20popped%20out.%20I%20threw%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Nathan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20broke.%20The%20suction%2C%20the%20force%20of%20everyone%20pulling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr.%20Taylor%20was%20pulled%20out%2C%20he%20had%20no%20pulse%2C%20and%20rangers%20began%20performing%20CPR%20before%20the%20paramedics%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Taylor%20was%20airlifted%20to%20Princess%20Alexandra%20Hospital%20in%20critical%20condition%20for%20further%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20understood%20it%20took%2045%20minutes%20before%20the%20man's%20pulse%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQAS%20Paramedic%20Peter%20Batt%20praised%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20people%20who%20helped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20they%20have%20got%20a%20return%20of%20pulse%20on%20this%20young%20man%20after%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20CPR%20is%20evidence%20that%20good%20CPR%20was%20being%20done%3B%20it's%20a%20credit%20to%20those%20people%20who%20got%20in%20and%20helped%20with%20their%20first%20aid%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20are%20now%20working%20to%20save%20the%20man's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701687780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fptoddhc_josh-taylor_625x300_04_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%