ve%20bite%20wound%20on%20her%20leg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Protection%20workers%20and%20firefighters%20in%20the%20municipality%20of%20Cihuatlan%2C%20which%20Melaque%20Beach%20is%20part%20of%2C%20said%2C%20''Our%20officials%20were%20carrying%20out%20support%20activities%20during%20a%20swimming%20event%20in%20the%20bay%20when%20they%20received%20reports%20of%20a%20person%20who%20was%20having%20problems%20getting%20out%20of%20the%20sea.%20When%20they%20reached%20the%20area%20they%20discovered%20a%20woman%20who%20was%20lifeless%20with%20one%20of%20her%20legs%20amputated%2C%20apparently%20following%20a%20shark%20attack.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20tragedy%2C%20local%20authorities%20issued%20a%20warning%20to%20locals%20and%20visitors%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20water.%20Organisers%20suspended%20a%20swimming%20race%20due%20to%20take%20place%20in%20the%20same%20waters.%20They%20also%C2%A0closed%20the%20beaches%20in%20Melaque%20and%20Barra%20de%20Navidad%20to%20swimming%20as%20a%20precaution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECihuatlan's%20municipal%20government%20said%20in%20a%20subsequent%20message%2C%20''Following%20the%20terrible%20incident%20off%20one%20of%20our%20beaches%2C%20our%20priority%20is%20guaranteeing%20the%20safety%20and%20wellbeing%20of%20all%20our%20citizens.%20That's%20why%20we've%20decided%20on%20a%20precautionary%20measure%20of%20banning%20access%20to%20beaches%20until%20further%20notice.%20We%20are%20working%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20appropriate%20authorities%20to%20evaluate%20the%20situation%20and%20take%20the%20necessary%20measures%20to%20guarantee%20security%20on%20our%20beaches.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701685920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2Fh4breu98_shark-attack-generic-pixabay_625x300_11_November_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-dies-after-shark-rips-off-her-leg-in-front-of-her-daughter-on-mexican-bea