world%2Frest-of-world%2Ftwo-dead-10-missing-after-indonesia-floods-and-landslide%2Famp_articleshow%2F105725652.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftwo-dead-10-missing-after-indonesia-floods-and-landslide%2Famp_articleshow%2F105725652.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Decomposing%20Bodies%20of%20Four%20Babies%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Grim%20Reminder%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20War%20That%20Has%20Not%20Spared%20Children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27090342%2Fimage1170x530cropped-6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20Gazan%20journalist%20ventured%20into%20the%20hospital%20to%20find%20an%20awful%20visual%3A%20decomposing%20bodies%20of%20four%20babies%2C%20eaten%20by%20worms%2C%20blackened%20by%20mold%2C%20mauled%20by%20stray%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Nasr%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Hospital%20director%20Bakr%20Qaoud%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20at%20the%20height%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20assault%20on%20northern%20Gaza%20in%20November%2C%20everybody%20was%20ordered%20to%20evacuate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20infants%2C%20born%20premature%2C%20were%20not%20known%20after%20a%20month%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20total%20of%20five%20infants%20Qaoud%20was%20taking%20care%20of.%20All%20of%20them%20were%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20needed%20oxygen%2C%20and%20medication%20administered%20at%20regular%20intervals.%20There%20were%20no%20portable%20respirators%20or%20incubators%20to%20transport%20them.%20Without%20life%20support%2C%20the%20nurse%20feared%2C%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20survive%20an%20evacuation%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Force%20delivered%20an%20ultimatum%20on%20November%2010%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F12%2F03%2Fgaza-premature-babies-dead-nasr%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20no%20choice%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20to%20carry%20the%20baby%20he%20thought%20will%20survive%20with%20a%20temporary%20cut%20to%20his%20oxygen%20supply.%20He%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20other%20four%20babies%2C%20reluctantly%2C%20with%20their%20breathing%20machines%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20forces%20told%20al-Nasr%E2%80%99s%20staff%20they%20had%20to%20leave%2C%20according%20to%20Qaoud.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20sent%20us%20a%20map%20for%20a%20safe%20route%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20WhatsApp%20message.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20gave%20us%20half%20an%20hour%20to%20go%20out.%20Otherwise%2C%20they%20will%20bombard%20the%20hospital.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20staff%20was%20promised%20that%20ambulances%20will%20be%20sent%20back%20to%20take%20the%20patients%20from%20al-Nasr%20and%20al-Rantisi%2C%20a%20pediatric%20cancer%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20telephone%20conversation%20with%20the%20Coordinator%20of%20Government%20Activities%20in%20the%20Territories%2C%20an%20arm%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20defense%20ministry%2C%20the%20al-Rantisi%20official%20requested%20ambulances.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fidfofficial%2F5131%5C%22%3Erecording%20of%20that%20call%20released%20by%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20%3C%2Fa%3EForces%2C%20a%20senior%20COGAT%20officer%20responds%20in%20Arabic%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20senior%20COGAT%20officer%20tells%20the%20al-Rantisi%20official%20that%20he%20will%20%E2%80%9Carrange%20coordination%E2%80%9D%20for%20ambulances.%20He%20gives%20the%20precise%20route%20that%20medical%20staff%20should%20take%20out%20of%20the%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20al-Rantisi%20official%20reminds%20COGAT%20that%20staff%20will%20also%20be%20evacuating%20al-Nasr.%20The%20COGAT%20officer%20acknowledges%20the%20reminder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EQaoud%2C%20too%2C%20said%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccoordination%20with%20the%20Red%20Cross%20and%20Israeli%20army%20that%20we%20will%20go%20out%20and%20then%20these%20cases%20will%20be%20later%20evacuated%20to%20another%20hospital%20that%20was%20safe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fnews%2F2023%2F12%2F01%2Fbirth-and-death-intertwined-gaza-strip%5C%22%3EHuman%20Rights%20Watch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gaza%20authorities%20said%20that%20more%20than%206%2C000%20Palestinian%20children%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20since%20the%20Hamas-led%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20There%20are%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fprogram%2Finside-story%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fwhy-have-so-many-palestinian-children-been-killed-by-israel%5C%22%3Ewho%20are%20still%20missing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20buried%20under%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Israeli%20authorities%2C%20the%20October%207%20attack%20killed%20at%20least%2033%20children%2C%20and%2040%20children%20were%20taken%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-the-world-watches-gaza-has-become-a-graveyard-for-children%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20World%20Watches%2C%20Gaza%20Has%20Become%20a%20Graveyard%20for%20Children%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOf%20what%20were%20the%20babies%20guilty%3F%20Why%20did%20the%20army%20target%20them%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20journalist%2C%20%3Cspan%20data-qa%3D%5C%22author-name%5C%22%3EHazem%20Balousha%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20described%20the%20scene%20on%20camera%20and%20hurried%20out%20of%20the%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20nurse%2C%20who%20reviewed%20the%20video%2C%20said%20the%20corpses%20were%20found%20where%20he%20had%20left%20the%20babies.%20No%20one%20had%20come%20for%20them%2C%3Cem%3E%20The%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20remains%2C%20still%20hooked%20up%20to%20respirators%2C%20bear%20little%20resemblance%20to%20bodies.%20They%20appear%20as%20piles%20of%20rotting%20flesh%2C%20bones%20protruding%2C%20body%20parts%20difficult%20to%20make%20out.%20Soiled-looking%20diapers%20remain%20wrapped%20around%20their%20middles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20IDF%20spokeswoman%20Doron%20Spielman%2C%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fspaces%2F1BRJjPOzoYaKw%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ea%20live%20conversation%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20appeared%20to%20cast%20doubt%20on%20the%20story%2C%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20no%20premature%20babies%20that%20decomposed%20because%20of%20the%20IDF%3B%20there%20were%20probably%20no%20babies%20that%20decomposed%20whatsoever.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20evacuation%20was%20painful.%20There%20was%20no%20way%20to%20reach%20the%20babies%E2%80%99%20families%2C%20the%20nurse%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20no%20contact%20information%2C%20and%20communications%20were%20disrupted%20in%20m