%20in%20the%2023-60%20years%20age%20group%20receive%20Rs%201%2C000%20every%20month%20in%20their%20bank%20accounts.%20This%20amount%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%2C%20will%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20gradually.%20The%20objective%20is%20to%20make%20women%20self-reliant%20and%20also%20empower%20them%20to%20address%20their%20health%20and%20nutrition%20requirements%20by%20providing%20them%20financial%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho's%20Eligible%2C%20Who's%20Not%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarried%20women%20residents%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20the%2023-60%20years%20age%20group%20are%20eligible%20to%20avail%20the%20scheme's%20benefit.%20This%20includes%20widows%2C%20divorced%20and%20abandoned%20women%2C%20according%20to%20the%20scheme's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20from%20families%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20more%20than%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20are%20not%20eligible%20for%20the%20scheme's%20benefits.%20Women%20who%20are%20income%20tax%20payers%20or%20whose%20family%20members%20are%20government%20employees%20are%20also%20ineligible.%20Unmarried%20women%20cannot%20avail%20of%20the%20scheme%20either.%20Women%20whose%20family%20members%20are%20elected%20public%20representatives%20cannot%20avail%20the%20benefits.%20If%20a%20woman%20is%20already%20receiving%20an%20amount%20less%20than%20Rs%201%2C000%20under%20any%20other%20scheme%2C%20the%20difference%20will%20be%20paid%20to%20her%20under%20the%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20scheme.%20The%20scheme%20also%20stands%20out%20because%20the%20monthly%20instalments%20would%20only%20get%20deposited%20in%20her%20account%20and%20not%20that%20of%20her%20husband%20or%20any%20other%20relative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fige9sgu_ladli-behna_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Implementation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040-member%20team%20involved%20in%20implementing%20the%20scheme%20pulled%20off%20a%20Herculean%20task%20by%20registering%201.25%20crore%20women%20under%20the%20scheme%20and%20crediting%20the%20assistance%20monthly%20in%2099%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20accounts%2C%20all%20within%20just%20100%20days.%20This%20was%20achieved%20through%20hundreds%20of%20camps%20set%20up%20for%20the%20registration.%20There%20would%20be%20long%20queues%2C%20but%20the%20process%20would%20take%20just%20minutes%2C%20even%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhijit%20Agarwal%2C%20Managing%20Director%20of%20MP%20State%20Electronics%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%2C%20said%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20scheme's%20implementation%20was%20the%20Aadhaar%20database.%20At%20the%20camps%2C%20the%20women's%20bank%20accounts%20would%20be%20linked%20to%20their%20phone%20numbers%20and%20Aadhaar.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20KYC%20process%20was%20completed%2C%20the%20data%20would%20come%20to%20us.%20This%20would%20also%20reduce%20the%20chance%20of%20human%20error%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fm7ucv3f8_ladli-behna_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Team%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20has%20over%2023%2C000%20panchayats%20and%20over%207%2C000%20wards.%20The%20team%20of%2040%20members%20completed%20registration%20of%20over%20a%20crore%20women%20within%20three%20months.%20Members%20of%20the%20team%20said%20that%20on%20some%20days%2C%20data%20of%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20women%20was%20being%20uploaded%20on%20the%20registration%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gurjar%2C%20an%20engineer%20part%20of%20the%20team%2C%20said%20they%20would%20work%2016-20%20hours%20a%20day.%20%26quot%3BEver%20since%20this%20project%20started%2C%20we%20worked%20tirelessly.%20We%20skipped%20every%20festival.%20We%20tried%20to%20work%20even%20if%20we%20were%20sick%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shivani%2C%20another%20engineer%20on%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fr13skheg_shivraj-chouhan_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Congress%20announced%20a%20monthly%20assistance%20of%20Rs%201%2C500%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20tweaked%20the%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20policy%20and%20hiked%20the%20monthly%20amount%20to%20Rs%201%2C250.%20Chief%20Minister%20Chouhan%20also%20said%20this%20amount%20would%20be%20increased%20gradually%20and%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Mukhya%20Mantra%20Ladli%20Behna%20Yojana%20has%20started%20with%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20stop%20there.%20Your%20brother%20will%20keep%20increasing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20then%20said.%20Congress's%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20then%20said%20this%20was%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20save%20its%20%26quot%3Bsinking%20ship%26quot%3B%20and%20stressed%20that%20it%20won't%20work%2C%20but%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20confident.%20Even%20a%20day%20after%20the%20election%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said%20the%20scheme%20was%20removing%20all%20thorns%20from%20the%20BJP's%20way%20to%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20Worked%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme's%20launch%20could%20be%20a%20political%20move%20in%20a%20poll%20year.%20But%20it%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20why%20it's%20crucial%20in%20a%20state%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20why%20it%20could%20potentially%20swing%20women%20votes.%20According%20to%20National%20Health%20and%20Family%20Survey%20data%2C%2023%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20in%20the%2015-49%20years%20age%20group%20have%20a%20body%20mass%20index%20lower%20than%20normal.%20Nearly%2055%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20in%20this%20age%20group%20are%20anaemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20about%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20in%20the%20state%20own%20house%2Fland%20individually%20or%20jointly.%20Only%2038.5%20women%20in%20the%20state%20have%20a%20mobile%20phone%20of%20their%20own.%20The%20number%20of%20women%20in%20the%20state's%20workforce%2C%20both%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas%2C%20are%20also%20dismal.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20a%20scheme%20that%20puts%20money%20in%20their%20hands%20can%20potentially%20help%20them%20better%20care%20of%20themselves.%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20also%20ensured%20that%20the%20amount%20did%20not%20go%20to%20a%20male%20relative%20-%20a%20system%20that%20has%20often%20been%20misused.%20The%20scheme%20worked%20for%20women%20and%2C%20as%20the%20results%20showed%2C%20for%20the%20BJP%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701681060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fnj1h9lqg_ladli-behna_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivraj-singh-chouhan-ladli-behna-madhya-pradesh-election-2023-why-ladli-behna-became-shivraj-chouhans-masterstroke-in-election-year-4632153%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20BJP%20swept%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20election%2C%20the%20result%20flying%20in%20the%20face%20of%20exit%20poll%20predictions%2C%20the%20spotlight%20is%20on%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government's%20welfare%20schemes%20such%20as%20'Ladli%20Behna'%20that%20helped%20BJP%20tap%20into%20women%20votes%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivraj-s