ct%2C%20Asalie%20was%20a%20rapper%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20and%20a%20pioneer%20of%20Hip%20Hop%20in%20Nagaland.%20But%20frustrated%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20support%20system%2C%20he%20traded%20in%20his%20mic%20for%20other%20pursuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInfinity%20Inc.%20stemmed%20from%20my%20short%20stint%20as%20a%20rapper%20earlier%20in%20the%202000s.%20The%20lack%20of%20a%20support%20system%20made%20it%20almost%20impossible%20for%20local%20artists%20to%20break%20out.%20Of%20course%2C%20social%20media%20was%20not%20even%20around%20at%20the%20time.%20These%20experiences%20inspired%20me%20to%20create%20Infinity%20Inc.%20%E2%80%94%20a%20springboard%20for%20upcoming%20Naga%20artists%20to%20reach%20the%20levels%20that%20they%20are%20capable%20of%20doing.%20At%20present%2C%20we%20have%20four%20artists%2C%20three%20DJs%20and%20two%20producers%20who%20are%20signed%20to%20our%20label%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEver%20since%20I%20started%20Infinity%20Inc.%20in%20February%202018%2C%20our%20priority%20was%20to%20sign%20Moko%20as%20an%20artist.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20appreciated%20that%20his%20art%20stems%20from%20his%20love%20of%20his%20culture%20and%20people%20and%20is%20marked%20by%20originality%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rare%20commodity%20in%20artists%20these%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Asalie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Moko%20remembers%20the%20call%20he%20received%20from%20Asalie%20following%20his%20post-graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20call%2C%20Assalie%20told%20me%20how%20they%20wanted%20to%20sign%20me%20as%20an%20artist.%20Without%20any%20second%20thoughts%2C%20I%20signed%20with%20them%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20music.%20Joining%20Infinity%20Inc.%20gave%20me%20access%20to%20a%20professional%20studio%20with%20in-house%20producers%20and%20sound%20engineers%20who%20would%20help%20me%20make%20the%20music%20I%20wanted.%20From%20struggling%20early%20on%20to%20put%20out%20music%20and%20asking%20my%20mother%20for%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20studio%20session%2C%20today%20I%20have%20access%20to%20the%20tools%20I%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Moko.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvincing%20his%20parents%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20hard.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20told%20them%20that%20I%20am%20going%20with%20music%20full-time%20and%20moving%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F240763%2Fnagaland-shiitake-oyster-mushrooms-earns-lakhs-how-to-grow-spores-method-scientist-innovation-agritech-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDimapur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20said%20that%20I%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20make%20my%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nagaland's%20growing%20Hip%20Hop%20community%20has%20Moko%20Koza%20at%20the%20front%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMoko%20Koza%20receiving%20the%20TaFMA%20Excellence%20Award%20(Left)%3B%20At%20a%20location%20for%20his%20music%20video%20(Right)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAse%20emi%20ekta%20Naga%20Manu%20chokora%20(First%20off%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20Naga)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ED-Block%2C%20Kohima%20town%20jonom%20hoa%20laga%20jaga%20(D-Block%2C%20Kohima%20town%20was%20where%20I%20was%20born)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAma%20laga%20peth%20para%20ula%20bole%20time%20te%20(As%20I%20came%20out%20from%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20womb)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%20khoom%20tu%20bukhi%20kena%20olaisheh%20(The%20blood%20of%20a%20Naga%20has%20been%20in%20me%20ever%20since)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20releasing%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20August%202022%2C%20Moko%20Koza%20caught%20the%20ears%20of%20Hip%20Hop%20aficionados%20from%20around%20the%20country%20with%20his%20battle%20rap%20songs%20and%20cyphers%20marked%20by%20interesting%20wordplay%2C%20flow%20and%20cadence.%20But%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20really%20put%20him%20on%20the%20map.%20The%20inspiration%20came%20from%20his%20memory%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPuisa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20first%20Nagamese%20song%20he%20put%20out%2C%20and%20the%20good%20reception%20it%20got%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPuisa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20means%20money%20in%20Nagamese%2C%20reflects%20on%20how%20the%20youth%20are%20exhausted%20by%20systemic%20corruption%20that%20has%20afflicted%20Nagaland%20for%20decades.%20Nagamese%20is%20the%20commonly%20accepted%20lingua%20franca%20in%20a%20state%20with%20many%20tribes%20that%20have%20their%20own%20indigenous%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EPuisa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20good%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20making%20more%20Nagamese%20songs.%20Writing%20and%20rapping%20in%20Nagamese%20and%20other%20dialects%20has%20introduced%20me%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20audience%2C%20particularly%20the%20older%20generations.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20I%20recognised%20that%20not%20everyone%20has%20the%20voice%20to%20speak%20for%20the%20community.%20As%20an%20artist%2C%20I%20have%20that%20platform.%20So%2C%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20address%20some%20key%20social%20issues%20in%20Nagaland%20like%20alcohol%20prohibition%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Moko.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20we%20talk%20about%20something%20very%20serious%2C%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20usually%20listen.%20So%20I%20thought%20of%20bringing%20in%20some%20humour%20so%20that%20people%20would%20listen.%20This%20helped%20me%20establish%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20song%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FvylA2NHVCIo%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FvylA2NHVCIo%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20song%20exposed%20a%20whole%20new%20audience%20to%20Moko%E2%80%99s%20music%20and%20provided%20some%20interesting%20insights%20into%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20%3Ca%20re