ative%20is%20set%20to%20harvest%20its%20second%20batch%20in%20the%20upcoming%20December%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESix%20tips%20for%20beginners%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20group%20was%20able%20to%20generate%20a%20handsome%20profit%20in%20their%20very%20first%20attempt%2C%20the%20success%20rate%2C%20Sanjay%20says%2C%20was%20not%20as%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20progressive%20farmer%20travelled%20to%20Bhubaneswar%20%E2%80%94%201%2C400%20km%20from%20his%20village%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20formal%20training%20in%20oyster%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F232818%2Fpearl-cultivation-earns-lakhs-urban-garden-cultured-freshwater-pearls-online-classes-business-how-to-ser106%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20attended%20a%20seven-day%20training%20at%20the%20Central%20Institute%20for%20Freshwater%20Aquaculture%20(CIFA)%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20how%20to%20source%20raw%20material%2C%20how%20to%20nucleate%20oysters%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20pearl%20designs%20that%20are%20in%20demand%2C%20what%20food%20to%20offer%20oysters%2C%20the%20surgical%20procedure%20of%20pearls%2C%20how%20to%20keep%20oysters%20in%20antibiotics%2C%20and%20what%20is%20its%20lifecycle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cooperative%20is%20set%20to%20harvest%20its%20second%20batch%20in%20the%20upcoming%20December%20month.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads